com.producttracker.entity

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.producttracker.entity.User

  • @Entity(name="users")
public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    The Food Inventory Tracker program outputs an inventory management web application for internal use by a restaurant. It implements a food expiration web service to get a food expiration duration. User roles are in place. Registered users are able to add tasks, update the current quantity of a product, and view products, categories, and vendors. Only admin are allowed to completely update a product; add/delete products, categories, and vendors. Only admin may view/update/delete the users list. A registered user may request admin privileges by filling out the contact form. A class to represent a user.
